    content: "# Contenido sobre sitios Web\n\nSe encuentra en la videoteca\n\nLinks\n\n[https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2169684340](https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2169684340)\n\n[https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2169863302](https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2169863302)\n\n[https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2188011510](https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2188011510)\n\n[https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2170885050](https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2152472987/posts/2170885050)\n\n[https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2153482988/posts/2170947775](https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2153482988/posts/2170947775)\n\n[https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2153482988/posts/2172836509](https://www.synergyforeducation.com/products/videoteca-de-lunes-sinergetico-y-miercoles-especialista/categories/2153482988/posts/2172836509)\n\n***NOTA: Puede que al momento de la consulta ya existan más utilizar el buscador en la videoteca para encontrar los actuales***\n\nEn la parte de arriba de la pagina aparece la opción “Buscar”",
